==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ingrown
<hw>In"grown`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having grown or
appearing to grow into some other substance, especially a fingernail or
toenail growing into the adjacent flesh.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Ingrown toenail</b></col>, <cd>a toenail whose edges have
becoming imbedded in the adjacent flesh.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ingrowth</ent>⟦br⟧
